flowchart LR
    faculty[Faculty / Staff]
    chair[Department Chair]
    qa[QA Officer / QA Admin]
    evaluator[Evaluator]
    admin[Superadmin / System Administrator]

    system[DocuDB Document Management System]

    db[(MongoDB Database)]
    storage[(Document File Storage)]
    email[SMTP Email Service]

    faculty -->|login, upload files, manage folders,\nshare documents, respond to requests| system
    chair -->|review submissions, approve or reject,\nassign folder tasks| system
    qa -->|quality assurance review, tagging,\ncompliance checks, workflow monitoring| system
    evaluator -->|view approved COPC packages,\nevaluation and reporting| system
    admin -->|manage users, roles, groups,\nlogs, analytics, and system settings| system

    system -->|stores users, metadata, versions,\ncomments, notifications, logs| db
    system -->|saves uploaded files,\npreviews, generated reports| storage
    system -->|sends account and activity\nnotification emails| email
